{"tid":694700,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"QS大學排名  台灣所有大學遭英機構誤植五星旗　台外交部要求更正","createTime":"2018-06-08T14:28:33.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-09T02:27:03.000Z","uid":35790,"like":1,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"f03709ea8f62aaa5cf14f2cc90c3716e0df7db12","tid":694700,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-08T14:28:33.000Z","msg":"我大學排名遭英機構誤植五星旗　外交部要求更正<br />\n<br />\n出版時間：2018/06/08 17:45<br />\n<br />\n有關英國QS 2019最新世界大學排名網站，台灣共17所大學進入全球千大排行，不過，卻遭植入中國五星旗，中華民國政府外交部今天表示，外交部已於第一時間要求我駐英國代表處進洽此機構要求即予更正。英國駐台辦事處回應，QS為一家私人公司。英國政府隨時為在海外營運之公司提供建議。。<br />\n<br />\n外交部重申，我政府堅定捍衛我國格及國家尊嚴的立場，不容任何挑戰；也再次提醒國際社會，中國政府向各國企業及文教機構強行輸出政治審查的蠻橫行徑，絕不應被忽視或縱容，否則民主、自由、人權等普世價值，將遭受嚴重侵蝕。<br />\n<br />\n外交部呼籲各國政府，企業及公民社會應立刻挺身而出，團結民主國家力量，採取一致立場，以積極具體的行動，與台灣一起共同維護共享的普世價值，讓國際社會免於中國威嚇脅迫。<br />\n（陳培煌/台北報導）<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.news.appledaily.com/politics/realtime/20180608/1369826/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.appledaily.com%2Fpolitics%2Frealtime%2F20180608%2F1369826%2F&d=E4ILr%2BITO37y6XHO142KSUkviAvgRC9mxyv2vFgVDqU%3D&h=98ae850f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.appledaily.com%2Fpolitics%2Frealtime%2F20180608%2F1369826%2F&h=348333da\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.news.appledaily.com/politics/realtime/20180608/1369826/</a>"},{"pid":"4d753563c4bb61cb9f5074eadf534bb80789d065","tid":694700,"uid":35790,"like":2,"dislike":4,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-08T14:33:06.000Z","msg":"台校全被QS大學排行標五星旗　教部要各校齊抗議<br />\n<br />\n建立時間：2018/06/08 16:27<br />\n<br />\n英國全球高等教育分析機構QS（Quacquarelli Symonds）日前公布2019年最新世界大學排名，台灣共有17校進入全球千大。然而，近日QS官網將台灣的大學旁中華民國國旗圖示，改為中國的五星旗。教育部對此提出嚴正抗議，並表示已聯絡駐英國代表處教育組，立即以電話及信函並行向QS抗議，要求立即更正；本次獲列名的台灣各所大學，一樣也將向QS提出抗議及請其更正。<br />\n（生活中心／台北報導）<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20180608/640_7de255c41abb5800015749b4bfc2164f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20180608%2F640_7de255c41abb5800015749b4bfc2164f.jpg&h=ab3fd918&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/new/realtime/20180608/1369736/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fnew%2Frealtime%2F20180608%2F1369736%2F&d=E4ILr%2BITO37y6XHO142KSUkviAvgRC9mxyv2vFgVDqU%3D&h=8966dfe3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fnew%2Frealtime%2F20180608%2F1369736%2F&h=b771c440\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/new/realtime/20180608/1369736/</a>"},{"pid":"c57a15c2c1d9b0f1682d4ed1ef4d8892e584c8ce","tid":694700,"uid":34103,"like":5,"dislike":41,"score":-36,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-06-08T14:37:30.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"dade30b1ec2dd049db40c803fe3a8545b4ad2816","tid":694700,"uid":69794,"like":27,"dislike":4,"score":23,"quote":{"pid":"c57a15c2c1d9b0f1682d4ed1ef4d8892e584c8ce","tid":694700,"uid":34103,"like":5,"dislike":41,"score":-36,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-06-08T14:37:30.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-08T14:49:16.000Z","msg":"標錯國旗邊個國家都會嘈ga啦，死開啦五毛狗"},{"pid":"a94959988c0f0dd11b5392849dcfd52d36b20aae","tid":694700,"uid":102609,"like":18,"dislike":2,"score":16,"quote":{"pid":"c57a15c2c1d9b0f1682d4ed1ef4d8892e584c8ce","tid":694700,"uid":34103,"like":5,"dislike":41,"score":-36,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-06-08T14:37:30.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-08T14:51:27.000Z","msg":"試下香港區旗消失<br />\n清一色變晒贏國旗<br />\n到時睇下你有咩反應？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e9db54fb218073dbda1124bf95c2b94a33107ba8","tid":694700,"uid":176366,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"c57a15c2c1d9b0f1682d4ed1ef4d8892e584c8ce","tid":694700,"uid":34103,"like":5,"dislike":41,"score":-36,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-06-08T14:37:30.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-08T14:51:34.000Z","msg":"縮返入你老母個閪到啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  好撚戇鳩啊你"},{"pid":"8875f5316fab55ebe6321403eedc12ff6061b1da","tid":694700,"uid":20241,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"a94959988c0f0dd11b5392849dcfd52d36b20aae","tid":694700,"uid":102609,"like":18,"dislike":2,"score":16,"quote":{"pid":"c57a15c2c1d9b0f1682d4ed1ef4d8892e584c8ce","tid":694700,"uid":34103,"like":5,"dislike":41,"score":-36,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-06-08T14:37:30.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-08T14:51:27.000Z","msg":"試下香港區旗消失<br />\n清一色變晒贏國旗<br />\n到時睇下你有咩反應？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-08T14:52:31.000Z","msg":"不意外<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"01c6e0b95dd4ceccda104bdd895acbd116f48918","tid":694700,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-08T14:56:32.000Z","msg":"近期贏國頻頻向外國商業機構<br />\n強迫更改台灣名稱 加註中國"},{"pid":"f13db76342eced3caa94bb3a3bea17477692dbb7","tid":694700,"uid":35790,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-08T16:14:18.000Z","msg":"溝通有效！QS網站我大學撤五星旗 改列台灣<br />\n<br />\n2018-06-08 23:01聯合報 記者徐偉真╱即時報導<br />\n<br />\n英國QS 2019最新世界大學排名網站，原先將我國大學所屬國旗誤植為中國五星旗，目前網站已將五星旗撤下，網站上的所有大學後面的國旗都已撤下，改列國家名稱，台灣上榜的大學所列的國家都是台灣（Taiwan），在國家的選單選項中也有Taiwan這個選項。<br />\n<br />\nQS網站撤五星旗改列國名，外交部表示，我國駐英國代表處第一時間立刻和該機構聯繫，充分說明我方嚴正立場，該機構正面理性看待我方訴求，並即以Taiwan名稱取代原掛的中國五星旗。<br />\n<br />\n外交部表示，對該機構採取明快作為，立即更正對我不當標示的勇氣及善意深表謝意，也期盼其他國際機構及跨國企業也能秉持道德勇氣，抗拒中國的施壓霸凌。<br />\n&lt;聯合&gt;"},{"pid":"5c26592eaf7296ea1a5d3751229c10ad0343889f","tid":694700,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-08T16:44:44.000Z","msg":"等睇Taiwan及Hong Kong後被加China<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e40430262667dcf053dec465c65fabf62a322b1","tid":694700,"uid":95520,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"a94959988c0f0dd11b5392849dcfd52d36b20aae","tid":694700,"uid":102609,"like":18,"dislike":2,"score":16,"quote":{"pid":"c57a15c2c1d9b0f1682d4ed1e